<p><br></p>
<br><div>
<h3><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">Wegeoo, the online classifieds platform</span></h3>
<p>Everybody has, at least once in their lives searched for an apartment for sale or rent on the Internet.<br></p>
<p>And you probably wanted this property to be close to your office, close to your children's school or maybe in a specific area depending on your budget.</p>
<p>You probably browsed on classic online classifieds sites and the result didn't allow you to properly appreciate the proximity of the properties regarding your office, your children's school, your favourite neighbourhood...</p>
<p>Painful isn't it ?</p>
<p>What Wegeoo offers compared to other existent online classifieds websites is to display the results of your search directly on an interactive map. That makes your search easy and gives you&nbsp;a more intuitive view of the results.</p>
<p>We all want to know what is happening around us. That's why this concept can also be applied to jobs, trainings and internships, events, promotional offers and services&nbsp;searches around you.</p>
<p>So Wegeoo is an online classifieds platform, applicable to all these categories.</p>
<div>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p><img src="https://images.indiegogo.com/file_attachments/938523/files/20141017114027-IndieGogoIndex_en.jpg?1413571227" style="max-width:620px;"></p>
</div>
<div><br></div>
<div>
<h3><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">...and a completely free ads publishing platform as well</span></h3>
</div>
<p>Publishing ads is completely free for both individuals and professionals.</p>
<p>For professionals, it is possible to use Wegeoo publication services to automatically publish their ads.</p>
<p>Moreover, in order to help you find as many properties as you'd like, Wegeoo can automatically download ads using an&nbsp;external&nbsp;recovery data&nbsp;system. Indeed, several websites&nbsp;make their ads available for free.</p>
<p>To give some numbers, it is possible to recover thousands of ads per week per country and that's so many available pages on Wegeoo !<br></p>
<div>
<img src="https://images.indiegogo.com/file_attachments/919477/files/20141010072842-WegeooSchemaRSS.jpg?1412951322" style="max-width:620px;"><br>
</div>
<div>
<br>
</div>
<div><br></div>
<h3><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">...with income from advertising</span></h3>
<div>
<p>Wegeoo dedicates specific areas to advertising. Several sizes are available, from a 300x250px banner to a complete relook. These areas are located on different pages of the site.</p>
<p>Different offers are available depending on the advertisers' demands and needs. Wegeoo manages the display of these advertisings&nbsp;internally.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Rates are not yet defined since they will depend on the traffic and on the page rank. In the beginning, Wegeoo will be resorting to providers like Google Adsense to make up for the shortfall of advertisers.&nbsp;<br></p>
<p>Wegeoo will have tens of thousands of pages available and will be&nbsp;ready to have traffic and generate income.</p>
<p><br></p>
