<h3><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">For this, we need contributions...</span></h3>
<p>Promoting Wegeoo with some&nbsp;advertising campaigns is essential to launch the project, attract visitors, generate traffic. These campaigns will be visible on other websites and on social networks.</p>
<p>In order to accelerate the creation of Wegeoo, we will use the services of freelancers for the design and the development of smartphone and tablets applications.</p>
<p>Some of the costs can't be reduced but some others can, such as marketing and freelance expenses. However, reducing the freelance costs might delay the development of the smartphone and tablets apps.</p>
<p><br></p>
