<h3><span style="color: #2D6FAC;"><br></span></h3>
<h3><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">The team</span></h3>
<p><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">Pierre RAFFA </span>&nbsp;I am a senior web developer with a degree in graphics and development. Over-motivated et passionate about my job, I did show my skills in a French software development company in digital publishing (digital comics and magazines ) with a mix of project management and development.</p>
<p><span style="color: #2D6FAC;">Mélanie TAQUET ( supportrice )</span>&nbsp;I am originally a Montessori teacher, also very passionate about my job, but about other things as well such as languages (I can speak 4 fluently). This is how I ended up working with Pierre on the project, a big part of my job being the translation of the website and fundraising campaign. I also contribute to the creative side of the project, on how to develop it, adapt it to different countries, how to make it &nbsp;clear and accessible to future contributors, how to promote it...</p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(45, 111, 172); font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 30px; background-color: initial;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(45, 111, 172); font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 30px; background-color: initial;">About &nbsp;the perks</span><br></p>
<div>If you own a business, website, a blog, a Youtube channel, a Facebook page... we will be honoured to promote it for some defined time through our advertising campaigns.&nbsp;<span style="background-color: initial;">Various areas and banner sizes are available.</span>
</div>
